WorkItem.ClosedComment: Actually, the armory is near instant speed now. No other character import sources are planned at this time.
WorkItem.Description: It would be funky if we could import characters from other sources than The Armory, such as character profilers, or even an addon to generate a profile of "our own". The Armory isn't well-known for its speedy updates, and it would be considerate to people who don't always wear their tanking gear.
WorkItem.Summary: [Feature Request.LoadCharacter] Import item sets from other sources
